tasks.title: Deliver the One Ring to Mordor
tasks.description: Frodo must carry the One Ring to Mount Doom to destroy it.

tasks.title: Train with Yoda on Dagobah
tasks.description: Luke Skywalker must complete his Jedi training with Master Yoda.

tasks.title: Reclaim the throne of Gondor
tasks.description: Aragorn must unite the people of Gondor and claim his rightful place as king.

tasks.title: Confront Darth Vader
tasks.description: Luke Skywalker must confront his father, Darth Vader, and turn him back to the light side.

tasks.title: Protect the Fellowship
tasks.description: Legolas must use his archery skills to protect the Fellowship during their journey.

tasks.title: Defeat Emperor Palpatine
tasks.description: Luke and the Rebellion must defeat the Emperor to restore peace to the galaxy.

tasks.title: Guard the Mines of Moria
tasks.description: Gimli must ensure the safety of the Fellowship while passing through the mines.

tasks.title: Destroy the Death Star
tasks.description: Han Solo and the Rebellion must destroy the second Death Star before it's operational.

tasks.title: Defend Mordor
tasks.description: Sauron must ensure the defenses of Mordor to protect the One Ring.

tasks.title: Expand the Galactic Empire
tasks.description: Emperor Palpatine must secure more systems for the Empire's control.
